# SQL Analytics Framework â€” Joe & The Juice Case Study

This folder contains structured SQL queries used to replicate the analytics in the Power BI dashboard.

Each script is organised by business question to ensure reproducibility and clarity.

## 1. Revenue & Sales Performance
- Identify top-performing stores by revenue
- Compare revenue distribution across locations

## 2. Product Performance
- Identify best and worst performing products
- Evaluate strategic vs underperforming products

## 3. Store & Regional Analysis
- Compare store-level category performance
- Identify growth opportunities and revenue concentration

## 4. Temporal & Behaviour Analysis
- Compare weekend vs weekday demand
- Identify peak trading hours

## 5. Profitability & Margin Analysis
- Compare revenue vs profit by product category

## 6. Trend & Growth Analysis
- Identify product and store growth trends over time

Each query includes business insight comments to explain analytical purpose.
